    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Siobhán O’Grady</title>
    <description>Siobhán O’Grady is an Africa-focused journalist and two-time grant recipient from the International Women’s Media Foundation. She has lived in Morocco and Cameroon and reported from South Sudan, Eastern Congo and Senegal, among others. She was previously a staff writer at Foreign Policy magazine. Follow her on Twitter @siobhan_ogrady.
